Package: patientSimASCVD
Type: Package
Title: Example ASCVD Model for the patientSim Ecosystem
Version: 1.4.0
Authors@R: person("Jarrod", "Dalton", email = "daltonj@ccf.org", role = c("aut","cre"))
Description: Example atherosclerotic cardiovascular disease (ASCVD) model used to
    demonstrate the patientSim ecosystem. The package provides a simple,
    transparent patient-level simulation of ASCVD-related events, designed
    for instructional use and for illustrating Core, Forecast, and Validation
    workflows.
License: Proprietary
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    patientSimCore (>= 1.3.3),
    patientSimPrepare (>= 1.3.5),
    patientSimForecast,
    patientSimValidation,
    R6
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0), knitr, rmarkdown, dplyr, tidyr, tibble
VignetteBuilder: knitr
